data.description: Welcome to the Bloomfield neighborhood of Rosemount! This great townhome sits in beautiful area right next to Bloomfield Park and it's only a few minutes away from all the shops and restaurants you could want. The main level is highlighted by modern white cabinets, stainless appliances, and great open floorplan. The upper level has a cozy loft as well as 2 bedrooms including a huge primary bedroom with 2 big walk-in closets. Easy living is ready for you, come take a look.
